## ðŸ§  Overview
E-MEDS is a **web-based smart medicine delivery and management system** designed to optimize pharmacy order handling using **process scheduling algorithms** and **interactive map integration**.  

It integrates **FCFS, SJF, and Priority Scheduling** to manage customer medicine orders efficiently.  
The system also allows users to **locate nearby pharmacies** using an interactive **map interface** powered by **LeafletJS** and **OpenStreetMap**.

