## ðŸ§® Scheduling Algorithm Implementation (JavaScript)
```js
orders.sort((a, b) => {
  if (a.priority !== b.priority) return a.priority - b.priority;
  if (a.priority === 0) return a.arrival - b.arrival; // Emergency â†’ FCFS
  if (a.totalQty !== b.totalQty) return a.totalQty - b.totalQty; // SJF tie-breaker
  return a.arrival - b.arrival;
});
